TITLE: Client-Side Lit Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Setup for client-side usage of Lit Protocol, including connection initialization and management.
SOURCE: https://github.com/lit-protocol/docs/blob/main/docs/sdk/access-control/quick-start.md#2025-04-18_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
import * as LitJsSdk from "@lit-protocol/lit-node-client";
import { LIT_NETWORK } from "@lit-protocol/constants";

class Lit {
   litNodeClient;
   chain;

   constructor(chain){
     this.chain = chain;
   }

   async connect() {
      this.litNodeClient = new LitJsSdk.LitNodeClient({
        litNetwork: LIT_NETWORK.DatilDev,
      });
      await this.litNodeClient.connect();
   }
}

const chain = "ethereum";

let myLit = new Lit(chain);
await myLit.connect();
```

