TITLE: Instantiating Lit Node Client
DESCRIPTION: Creation and connection of LitNodeClient instance configured for the Datil test network.
SOURCE: https://github.com/lit-protocol/docs/blob/main/docs/paying-for-lit/using-delegated-auth-sig.md#2025-04-18_snippet_2

