TITLE: Generating Session Signature from Capacity Credit Delegation in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to generate a session signature for a PKP using a capacity credit delegation. It includes creating an auth callback, getting session signatures, and executing a JavaScript function to sign data.
