TITLE: Signing and Submitting Transactions in Lit Action using JavaScript and ethers.js
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to use signAndCombineEcdsa to combine partial signatures, create a complete signature, and submit a signed transaction using ethers.js within a Lit Action. It includes error handling and transaction receipt logging.
