TITLE: Displaying SDK Error Codes and Reasons for Serrano Version (Markdown)
DESCRIPTION: A markdown table listing error codes and their corresponding reasons for the 'serrano' version of the Lit Protocol SDK. It includes a wide range of error scenarios such as node system faults, authentication failures, and blockchain-related issues.
