TITLE: Including Feedback Component in Markdown
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet includes the imported FeedbackComponent at the end of the document. It's used to render a feedback section for users.
SOURCE: https://github.com/lit-protocol/docs/blob/main/docs/sdk/serverless-signing/dependencies.md#2025-04-18_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: markdown
CODE:
```
